Author: vignt-trois
Text: I found [this](https://www.quora.com/If-I-tell-my-therapist-that-I-have-an-eating-disorder-is-she-required-to-tell-my-parents)  for you. In my opinion, I really think you should tell her. Easier said than done, I know, but you don’t want to look back at this years from now wishing that you said something.❤️
